[Quick and Easy Assembly] With step-by-step instructions and labeled parts, you can set this cupboard up before you know it

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice! Easy to put together
reviews.reviewText: This was probably the quickest and easiest piece of furniture I’ve ever put together! Zero issues there and very little to put together.It’s mostly metal, only the top part is wood. It’s lighter weight but not flimsy or cheap feeling. Nothing was bent or damaged and all came easily together without a struggle. Good buy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love this. Bought it store color and random stuff for work. Fit all my color and toners plus more. Was super easy to put together did it in 30 minutes. Can easily wipe off any color on it without staining. Made of metal so very sturdy. Damage free very durable. Super cute and always gets compliments on it and where I got it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, but doors swing open
reviews.reviewText: First off, I am pretty happy with this. It feels very well made and the top wood panel feels like good quality. It was easy to assemble and fit perfectly in the corner I wanted it in. I love that I can change the height of the shelf inside and it looks so clean. My only issue is that the door doesn't latch well. It has a magnet latch but it must not be strong enough as the doors tend to swing open. I'll probably just see about adding on a magnetic child lock as I don't want my kitten getting into it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks Great and Easy to Assemble
reviews.reviewText: This arrived quickly and was very easy to assemble by myself. The instructions were very clear and easy to follow. It comes with a screw driver but does recommend using a power/electric screw driver. I followed that advice and it was quite simple to assemble. It looks great and seems sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are actually perfect. I use lighter colors in my home but my work desk is darker because of the theme we had in the room my desk was in before moving. I looked for 6 weeks at different options to store all the crafting stuff. I was on the verge of buying all new office furniture and then These popped up on Amazon. decided to give them a 2 of these.Wow! Great quality, easy to put together. They fit all the craft supplies I had and thinking of getting a 3rd one for my nail stuff.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and sturdy!
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to hide my weights and exercise equipment. All the weight storage racks look like weight storage racks and did not hide them at all! This cabinet is made of metal and is definitely study enough to hold my two 25 weights on the bottom shelf and my smaller hand weights on the top shelf! It also holds my yoga mat, work out shoes and everything else! My husband said it was easy to put together and all items were in the box. With doors closed, it doesn’t scream “home gym” in our family room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to put together
reviews.reviewText: I would not consider myself a very handy person, but I was able to put it together according to the directions on my own fairly easily! People mentioned issues about swinging doors— I just used the included plastic washers and it fixed that issue. I think it looks great in person (better than expected), and is very spacious. Adjustable feet are great, as is the adjustable shelf. It was also packaged very well! Only minor thing was that there are small imperfections (small blob of paint on the handle) but considering the price, I thought it was great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love it!
reviews.reviewText: Came very well packedInstructions are definitely lacking, hardware packets have no letters on them but instructions show hardware by the non-existent letters. But it was easy enough to figure out.Feels very well made, it’s all metal but has a “soft touch” feel to it and the wood top is heavy and substantial.No issues with doors coming open as mentioned in some reviews, but the magnetic closure isn’t very clear in the instructions so be sure it’s installed with the screws facing the doors.
Bought for our kitchen to store the extra appliances that clutter the counter. Worked perfectly for what we wanted. Matches our kitchen & looks great & easy to put together.
This sideboard is great. Easy to assemble. Doors close nicely. Very Sturdy, Would buy again!

Very spacious, love the look of it! The top is a nice touch to make it less industrial looking which is the perfect look I was going for. I store all my crafting items in it, and they fit the Michaels cheap storage bins that are always on sals very well, laying flat. It arrived before schedule, no issues with the packaging and went together easily :).
Looks good. Sturdy. Went together easy. Lots of storage space inside.

Purchased this unit to hold a sound mixing board. Very easy to construct and very solid once constructed. I added a locking device to the front, added a sliding shelf to the unit, and added a light inside the unit. This is working perfectly for our needs.
